Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, this is quite the bounded field.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks impossible to brute force yourself past it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect nothing less from something the Edelfelts own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored to receive such compliments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, not even the El-Melloi Princess can find a way to escape from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,From ancient times,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,various myths and legends have stated that wealth springs from underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Graves and the underworld have another aspect of being storehouses for treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you should hide your treasured collection under the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Like games, and those promissory notes in safes hidden in underground labyrinths!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And secrets adults hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But Professor, you have no need for such because you have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always okay with personal lectures, or rather I want to be your mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:01:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you guys, shut up right now or get triple the homework. Take your pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kings stockpiled immense fortunes in their graves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to continue their reign in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, the pharaohs of Egypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Babylonia's King of Heroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilgamesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll continue with the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,From ancient times, it has been said wealth springs from underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, you've already covered that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so? Sorry. Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he saw during the Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However, at the rate he's going,\Nhe will become roped into more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Grail War...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:52.05,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:21.93,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what'd you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're drawing this out.\NThere's something you want to ask, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's about your mentor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,my dear elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Master supposedly was a part of this Holy Grail War in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to him there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I don't mind talking to you about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's rather dull if I told you for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaining information requires a suitable compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you accompany me in my hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This does look good on you just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true! You can see my face, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. We're the only ones in the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,With over 150 years of tradition,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Carnac is one of London's biggest department stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As compensation, you agreed to come with me on my shopping trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all been about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need winter clothes soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will personally choose clothing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a bit too daring?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, a magus has to experience all things. Experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! This suits you more than I imagined, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They do say that clothes make the woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this commotion about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miss Luvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the owner of this establishment, Carnac.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this entire store belongs to Miss Luvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The original owner was Sir Davenant who was arrested in that incident the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The magus...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why the architecture is this strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's magecraft designed to stimulate customers' eagerness to purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I did change the interior decoration quite a bit to suit my aesthetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a little over the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I adapted some of my Gem Magecraft here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're both here, I'll give a personal tour of the newly reborn Carnac.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're being a bit pushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are bored, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that often where all three of us coincidentally gather in one location.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You're inviting us to a girls' party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. You're okay, too, right, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is a girls' party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, this is a bit too provocative?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Professor seems to still be a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{=1}{\pos(960,1028.68)}I mean, Professor seems to still be a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{=1}{\pos(960,1125.09)}I mean, Professor seems to still be a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it really is a bit over the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd ruin it for you if I were to buy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have a few things to take care of,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so please relax here in the owner's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was experiencing everything for the very first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was a bit overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,London is very stimulating, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in my homeland,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,there really was nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Luvia has stepped out, it's the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's chat about what you've been wanting to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A magecraft battle in the Far East,\Nfighting over the omnipotent wish granter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven magi and seven heroes famous through human history
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,serving them as Servants, fought each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of Servant did Master fight alongside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Iskandar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Also known as Alexander the Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's truly a ridiculous fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The supposed King of Conquerors
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,who created one of the most prominent empires in human history...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The King of Conquerors, Iskandar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite established among the great Heroic Spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably why my incompetent elder brother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,was able to survive through the Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly did Master see within that battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something even I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But a lad named Waver Velvet, who survived through the ordeal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,has chosen the path of suffering by inheriting the name "El-Melloi."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was such an important experience for Master that it changed his way of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, wanting to participate in another Holy Grail War...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My elder brother seems to be quite particular about that memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Reines?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A bounded field of the magical sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One so extraordinary that my Mystic Eyes\Nshow an excessive reaction to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this isn't one of your pranks, Luviagelita.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's not! I'll toss that line right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we should get out of this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Trimmau.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Check what's beyond the door, but do it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a type of alternate space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we've been severed from the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the other exits will behave the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean we're trapped in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But why just the three of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps an assassination attempt on the next head of the El-Melloi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a family that also has many enemies within the Clock Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, must have grudges for all the aggressive actions you've taken, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, let's think of a way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we contact anyone outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No electromagnetic waves have succeeded connection for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we must get through all of this by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you think we should bet on sitting here and waiting for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course the answer to that is "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make whoever planned such a ludicrous ordeal regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we're in agreement there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Call blue, red, green...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for your queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No good after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting rather annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This reminds me of what happened at the Separation Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Luvia, you got trapped inside a bounded field back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear the details about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I reject that request!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And Gray, don't say things you don't need to! Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're getting nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to open an escape route with magecraft we have on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, Master was with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If Master was here in a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, if said El-Melloi II was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be his forte, his specialty to dismantle such a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And fortunately, we know a little bit of how that man teaches. His logic, his tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do you mean we should try mimicking what Master might do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we can't figure out any other option.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who knows how he does things best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like this, what would the starting point for his logic be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be the whydunit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That means the motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were just the three of us trapped in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not even worth considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There are plenty of reasons why someone would target us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the two of you,\NI'm not that important a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a poor student
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,compared to these young ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this was a plan targeting one of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it's unnatural to get all three of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's strange they just captured us and haven't made any other actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it. Compared to how grand this bounded field is, it's somehow a sloppy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if the perpetrator isn't thinking at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What if there was no perpetrator\Nfrom the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, it wasn't like someone targeted us and locked us up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So, not an incident but merely an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're suggesting that the magical structure\Nof this building ran out of control?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying there were faults in the interior decorating that I adjusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of my family, I never used cheap spells that would do as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the reverse, "Owner."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that there was anything lacking,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was just too much,\N and it created an excessive reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you think of it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That just can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you have an idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,about what I'm talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong in this hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the building was enchanted with magecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,stimulating customers' eagerness to purchase, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The key element for the spell is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In magecraft, wealth springs from underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why we're in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Gem Magecraft?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, way too over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like getting carried away and putting way too many toppings on a parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hush, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, if we can somehow deal with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the security system is also running out of control?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that without you saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you stop it somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My systems are perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way outside intervention will be authorized!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Trim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll settle everything by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pro wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A graceful mannerism unleashes a\Ndepartment store full of murderous techniques!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A Scandinavian human forklift!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you could call her\N"Heracles revived in modern day"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that Flatt guy teaching Trim?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Catch-as-catch-can{\i0} is a game for the ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's what every lady should know about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't go believing her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need to do now is to break this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you fine with that? It must cost quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's inexpensive as the price for the lesson I learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At times, one must discard even things that are important in order to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even things that are important...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing less from the head of the Edelfelt family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Trimmau?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quite an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to celebrate our return...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we have another round of afternoon tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be careful about all the toppings I add on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We were involved in quite the trouble today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but somehow it ended up being fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's something I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was magecraft on a building running out of control,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,what caused it to activate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can at least make a theory in the fashion of my elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Carnac was enchanted with magecraft to gather a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it was a spell that didn't allow fortune to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't allow an escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. We were seen as treasures to not be taken outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it meant putting up a bounded field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can understand Miss Reines or Miss Luvia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the most mystic of Mystics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You carry one of the most prominent Noble Phantasms in human history!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez. Having low self-esteem can be questionable, too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this... He won't think this is strange or anything, will he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have returned, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like she took you around on quite a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry my little sister troubles you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...of utmost importance to me has been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A relic of a certain Heroic Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard from Reines, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heroic Spirit that I fought alongside in the Holy Grail War ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The mantle of Iskandar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The key for Master to reunite with said spirit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left inside the box that housed the relic was this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"We hereby invite you to our banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We request the pleasure of your company, so we hope that you will attend by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mystic Eyes Collection Train,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rail Zeppelin."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rail Zeppelin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It gathers any and every Mystic Eyes out there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and puts them on auction once a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A train full of supernatural beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, that's where...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you head out to Rail Zeppelin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,together with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:10.02,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Ending}
